cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with audio processing and keyword spotting. It could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it involves natural language processing and speech recognition. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses deep neural networks for training and prediction. It may also fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it involves designing an efficient system for keyword spotting. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks for keyword spotting.
